                                </h3>
                                <div class="featured-image">
                                    <a href="https://www.lasnaves.com/novatos20d-una-jornada-electoral/" target="_blank">
                                    <img class="img-responsive project-image" src="/assets/images/cabecera-landing.jpg" alt="project name" />
